   ```

## Context

- `LocalDispatcher` exists at `packages/agent-claude-sdk-runner/src/local-dispatcher.ts`. Its `execute()` method ALREADY wraps thrown errors with the tool name prefix (e.g. `local dispatcher: tool 'echo_local' failed: ...`). The "no registered executor" test relies on this ŌĆö `dispatcher.execute()` throws with the tool name when there's no registered executor.
